<!-- Release notes generated using configuration in .github/release.yml at 4.0.x -->

## What's new and breaking changes

- Kotlin 1.8
- [Experimental Support for Kotlin Symbol Processing (KSP)](https://docs.micronaut.io/snapshot/guide/#ksp)
- Apache Groovy 4.0
- [Support for Virtual Threads](https://docs.micronaut.io/snapshot/guide/#virtualThreads)
- [Filter Methods](https://docs.micronaut.io/snapshot/guide/#filtermethods)
- Injection of Maps
- Improved Error Messages for Missing Beans
- Tracking of Disabled Beans
- `micronaut-retry` dependency.
- `micronaut-discovery` dependency.
- `micronaut-websocket` dependency.
- Reactor instrumentation moved to Reactor module.
- Validation support moved to validatio module
- session support moved to session module. 
- kotlin flow support moved to kotlin module. 
- Compilation time Api split into a new module `micronaut-core-processor`
- ASM no longer shaded
- Caffeine no longer shaded
- Environment deduction disabled by default. 
- SnakeYAML no longer a direct dependency


## What's Changed
### Breaking Changes 🛠
* Make SnakeYAML and javax.annotation optional by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8061
* Refactor `ConversionService` to remove mutable operations from `ConversionService.SHARED` by @dstepanov in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8156
* Disable Cloud environment deduction by default. Fixes #7758 by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8068
* Rework BOM as core BOM by @melix in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8299
* Remove the session module, and add micronaut-session by @timyates in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8281
### New Features 🎉
* Virtual thread support by @yawkat in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8180
* Introduce `@Vetoed` to exclude particular classes, methods and fields from processing by @dstepanov in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8274
* Implement support for injection of maps by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8305
* Support arbitrary nesting of EachProperty/ConfigurationProperties beans by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8424
* Adds support for KSP by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8462
* Support annotation-based HTTP filter declarations by @yawkat in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8422
* Include disabled bean info in beans endpoint by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8792
* feat: HTTP Client Implementation with Java HTTP Client by @sdelamo in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8441
* HTTP/3 support by @yawkat in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8559
### Bug Fixes 🐞
* Remove use of shadow plugin by @melix in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8312
* Stop conversion of Properties keys and values by @timyates in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8327
* Groovy properties shouldn't become executable methods by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8350
* Fix bug in introspections when properties are of mixed types by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8451
* Don't include write only properties in serialization by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8457
* Fix bug with custom conditions and EachBean definitions by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8459
* Fix incorrect dependency substitution by @melix in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8467
* fix configuration inheritance path calculation by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8484
* Fix NonUniqueBeanException when using FunctionInitializer by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8488
* Remove usage of Utils classes from GraalReflectionConfigurer by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8563
* Pick a more specific setter if child configuration properties by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8578
* Fix NPE producing anntotion metadata for KSP by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8736
* Fix GraalVM native image support by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8793
* fix validation of write-only config properties by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8826
* Fix broken MethodElement.overrides implementation by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8842
* fix IncompatibleClassChangeError in ConfigurationProperties by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8864
* fix: WebSocketMessageEncoder @Requires classes by @sdelamo in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8962
### Improvements ⭐
* Stop repackaging Caffeine by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8054
* One channel per HTTP2 stream by @yawkat in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/6842
* Match interceptors by all the bindings it defines by @dstepanov in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8174
* Let SemanticVersion.isAtLeastMajorMinor be able to compare two different major versions. by @donbeave in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8208
* Reuse enclosed elements querying for Java and Groovy. Added a way to query methods and fields together. by @dstepanov in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8197
* HTTP Netty server executing route refactoring by @dstepanov in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8217
* Split the runtime and compiler code into separate modules by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8224
* Split the runtime module into multiple modules by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8235
* Class -> Class<?> by @altro3 in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8278
* Add support for Jakarta nulllable annotations.  by @baracil in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8307
* remove javax.annotation.Nullable usage by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8311
* Improve support for configuration property nesting by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8306
* Improve the error message for missing beans when EachBean is used by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8316
* Improve error messages for disabled beans by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8326
* Detect deadlocks when using BlockingHttpClient on the event loop by @yawkat in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8354
* Remove NoInjectBeanDefinition and improve/refactor RuntimeBeanDefinition by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8398
* Eliminate unused proxy targets and simplify resolution by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8447
* Add tests and refine behaviour of registerSingleton by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8469
* add isWithin(..) check to each property handling by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8565
* Support Range requests when returning SystemFiles by @kgeri in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8553
* Optimize HttpRequestCertificateHandler by @yawkat in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8771
* Refactor: Remove unnecessary use of reactive APIs in routes endpoint by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8795
* Remove more GraalVM build-time init flags by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8841
* cleanup unnecessary GraalVM flags by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8843
* Remove jackson databind as a transtive of GraalVM module by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8869
* Allow to introspect classes by names by @dstepanov in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8899
### Docs 📖

* doc: use asciidoc inner link by @sdelamo in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8732

* Update simple retry doc to mention a linear progression of 1s by @miguelaferreira in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8850
* Remove docs for HTTP sessions and provide link to `micronaut-session` docs by @wetted in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8737
* doc: delete what’s new and breaks prior to 4.0.0 by @sdelamo in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8952
* doc: add websocket dependency by @sdelamo in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8953
